Modo describuntur candelabra septem lucentia,
etc.  Paucum, idest paulo, ulterius, septem arbores auri
falsificabat in apparentia longus tractus (idest longa distantia
falsificabat; quia propter longum tractum, sive longam
distantiam, apparebant septem arbores auri, ubi in rei veritate
erant septem candelabra) medietatis, terre adhuc inter nos et
ipsas, vel dic aieris, quia aier erat inter potentiam visivam
Dantis et rem visam, idest candelabra.
